+  *    - ESP_ERR_INVALID_ARG: invalid argument
+  *    - ESP_ERR_WIFI_IF: invalid interface
+  *    - ESP_ERR_WIFI_MAC: invalid mac address
+  *    - ESP_ERR_WIFI_MODE: WiFi mode is wrong
+  *    - others: refer to error codes in esp_err.h
